        "Action Items": "- Send ROI framework for manufacturing IoT (reduce downtime, improve utilization)\n- Prepare pilot proposal for Detroit plant ($50K estimate)\n- Research MQTT and OPC-UA integration options for their equipment mix\n- Follow up in 2 weeks to check on business case progress",
