        "Raw Source": "> [!note]- Raw Source\n> # Meeting Notes — April 7, 2026\n>\n> **Meeting:** Follow-up call with NovaPay (intro from Tom Nakamura)\n> **Attendees:** Lisa Tran (CTO, NovaPay), Our Team\n> **Duration:** 30 minutes\n>\n> Lisa Tran is the CTO of NovaPay, a fintech startup building payment infrastructure for e-commerce platforms. They're a Coastal Ventures portfolio company — Tom Nakamura made the introduction.\n>\n> NovaPay needs real-time transaction analytics for their merchant dashboard. Currently they're using a homegrown solution that can't scale past 1M events/day. They need:\n> - Real-time event processing (sub-200ms)\n> - Merchant-facing analytics dashboard (white-labeled)\n> - PCI DSS compliance\n> - Pricing that scales with transaction volume\n>\n> Lisa said they have budget approved for Q2. She wants to see a demo next week and fast-track evaluation — they need a solution in place by June.\n>\n> NovaPay is Series A ($12M raised), 30 employees, based in New York. They serve ~500 e-commerce merchants.\n>\n> ## Action Items\n> - Schedule demo for next week (Lisa prefers Tuesday or Wednesday)\n> - Send PCI DSS compliance documentation\n> - Prepare fintech-specific pricing proposal\n> - Let Tom know the intro went well"
